Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易\N亮和達士多捷特才打成平手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.73,0:01:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但右手卻被砍掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夢妮為了復原亮的右手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將他放在水中的治療囊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行改造人手術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55\fad(200,200)\pos(480,680)}亮，站起來!\N超音戰士暗殺指令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的右手怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還不是自己的手似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著是繼續物理治療的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試握著我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我未習慣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠不住的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，觸覺好像回復了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只令一位超音戰士受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你的力量不過如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲魯美，你有什麼策略嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雲哥度餘下的\N最強妖魔機人坎比魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:03:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坎比魯斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，那坎比魯斯\N已前往米加羅城市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在妖魔機人之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最強的狙擊手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對於受傷的亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以坎比魯斯\N他是不堪一擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此小看亮，會丟掉性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小看的\N不是達士多捷特你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拭目以待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超音戰士到底是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候救我的超音戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是艾莉斯老師似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能超音戰士\N就是老師他們也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真兒，怎麼了?真兒...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真的留心上課
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因測驗的分數太低\N被媽媽罵了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，安靜點!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這桌子又舊又破的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙，還未能控制力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師是超音戰士?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見亮老師今天的怪力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可能真的是\N桌子太舊也不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀，我也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但欠缺膽量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，跟蹤他看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蹤老師嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會知道什麼秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對的事才是最有趣的\N去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說曹操，曹操便到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，開始跟蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮!來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，不用著急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那隻手才剛出世沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想這種狀態下\N如妖魔再來襲擊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如這樣下去\N連學生也保護不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師他們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是訓練嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為是運動不足的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為何要在那種地方才做?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在背後三百米，有妖魔反應!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖魔...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為何來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師，想想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!不能在這裡變身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，由你來駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你這樣，不能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡由我來想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶小孩到安全的地方躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想自己做英雄嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是這麼說的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊，這邊啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Borg Get On!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手是我!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!這樣是接近不了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何要到那地方去?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們跟蹤了老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蹤?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真兒不對呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，竟說老師們是超音戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你是超音戰士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼便去收拾妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積克他失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫救援\N你們不要離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去叫救援的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧\N老師們果然不是超音戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如是超音戰士\N便早已救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷電!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷電，來的真是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因我和你相交很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼便去迎接妖魔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Borg Get On!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷電，積克有聯絡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被困在廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!竟然弄成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖魔導彈!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!竟下這麼重手\N在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖魔探測器發生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能確定敵人的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我和艾莉斯他們聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，手腕發麻...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標確認
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這美男子竟弄成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接的車來了，時機真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積克，你沒事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮他們被妖魔襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已追蹤了雷電發訊的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖手腕不行，但我還有雙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行走速度，正負20
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如在這裡被打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了什麼去成為改造人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就失去意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了，喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型武器嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夢妮那傢伙，真有本事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難纏的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-亮!\N-不是很精神嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還有幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狠狠的被他玩弄了\N快解決掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，以你那身體是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他拿走了甜頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎?他沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，身體可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩們呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地下的停車場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟說老師們是超音戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是真兒的胡扯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀，因這樣而遇上危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還罰我們打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好超音戰士來救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎麼說好呢...以命運來說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的惡運很強\N能這樣來分析
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，老師們真的不是超音戰士嗎?
